window.bookSummaryJSON = "Maisie Dobbs is back, and this time she has been hired to find a wealthy grocery magnate's daughter who has fled from home. <p>What seems a simple case at first becomes complicated when Maisie learns of the recent violent deaths of three of the heiress's old friends. Is there a connection between her mysterious disappearance and the murders? Who would kill such charming young women?</p> <p> As Maisie investigates, she discovers that the answers to all her questions lie in the unforgettable agony of The Great War.</p>"; 
